        <title>关于我写博客如何实现闭环那些事</title>
        <link>https://singlebee.github.io/post/%E5%A5%B3%E5%A8%B2%E8%A1%A5%E5%A4%A9/%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%E6%88%91%E5%86%99%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E9%97%AD%E7%8E%AF%E9%82%A3%E4%BA%9B%E4%BA%8B/</link>
